[In the past, 1997 and 1999, the FMD type was serotype O, the same type
as Britain now has. I do not know what subtypes either of these outbreaks
are. However, earlier ProMED-mail posted a statement released in Britain
indicating this could be a pandemic version. - Mod.TG
